snippet.title: Kate Middleton & The Queen
snippet.description:
Hello and welcome to Kate Middleton & The Queen's news channel. Here we will send you not only news about the Duchess of Cambridge and Queen Elizabeth II but also information about Prince William, Prince Charles, Prince Harry and Meghan Markle. We will also provide you with the latest news on the royal children such as Prince George, Princess Charlotte, Prince Louis and Baby Archie. Follow us to get the latest news! Thank you!
Subscribe to my channel: http://bit.ly/35mL3xJ
